widgets_values: Golem figure made of sealant glued together with pink toothpaste. Visible seams filled with paste in kintsugi fashion. Human sillhouette has fuzzy foamy overall form. Head is abstract disfigurent sealant gummy blob with giant ears. Material is dusty and scuffed with visible imperfections and scratches. Crisp analog video. Japanese 1960s color grading. Shot with bright cimentatic backlight. The background is dental clinic with blue walls, old medical equipement, medical posters about teeth health.
